---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Process" description="Learn about Wellridge Advisory's systematic six-step process for grant and RFP success.">
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-fog">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-deep mb-6">Our Process</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        A repeatable, structured approach that reduces stress and increases win rates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Every successful proposal follows a clear path from initial discovery to post-award stewardship. Our six-step process ensures nothing falls through the cracks and every opportunity is evaluated with rigor and clarity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-fog">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-ridge-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
              1
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Discover</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                We start by understanding your organization, your programs, your funding goals, and your capacity. This includes reviewing your mission, strategic plan, current funding portfolio, and any existing case-for-support materials.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Deliverables:</strong> Discovery session notes, organizational profile, funding readiness assessment
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-ridge-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
              2
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Align</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                We conduct prospect research and create alignment scorecards that evaluate fit, capacity, and strategic value. Using our go/no-go rubric, we help you decide which opportunities are worth pursuing.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Deliverables:</strong> Prospect research report, alignment scorecard, go/no-go recommendation
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-ridge-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
              3
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Build</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                We develop the proposal architecture, narrative outline, and budget structure. This includes identifying evidence needs, gathering supporting materials, and creating a project calendar with clear milestones.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Deliverables:</strong> Proposal outline, narrative architecture, budget framework, project calendar
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-ridge-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
              4
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Write</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                We draft the full proposal, including narrative sections, budget narratives, and supporting documents. Throughout the process, we maintain regular communication and incorporate your feedback through structured revision cycles.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Deliverables:</strong> Draft proposal, budget narrative, supporting documents, revision cycles
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-ridge-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
              5
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Submit</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                We conduct a final compliance review, prepare all attachments, and manage the submission process. This includes red-team review, quality assurance checks, and ensuring every requirement is met.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Deliverables:</strong> Final proposal package, compliance checklist, submission confirmation
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-ridge-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
              6
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Steward</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                After submission, we help you manage the relationship with the funder, prepare for potential site visits or interviews, and develop renewal strategies. For awarded grants, we support reporting and ongoing stewardship.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Deliverables:</strong> Post-submission debrief, renewal strategy, reporting support (if awarded)
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">Our Tools</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Throughout the process, we use systematic tools to ensure quality and consistency:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
        <li><strong>Alignment Scorecards:</strong> Evaluate funder fit and strategic value</li>
        <li><strong>Go/No-Go Rubric:</strong> Quick decision framework for opportunity evaluation</li>
        <li><strong>Red-Team Memos:</strong> Critical review from a funder's perspective</li>
        <li><strong>Compliance Checklists:</strong> Ensure every requirement is met</li>
        <li><strong>Project Calendars:</strong> Clear milestones and deadlines</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-6">
        Many of these tools are available in our <a href="/resources" class="text-ridge-blue hover:underline">Resources</a> section.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-deep text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">Ready to See It in Action?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Schedule a walkthrough of our process and see how we can help you win more grants.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-ridge-blue text-white rounded-md text-lg font-medium hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-colors"
      >
        Schedule a Walkthrough
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

